<br>
The people like myself that have already spent a considerable amount of time in the planes acquiring good armor are being punished if we are continually forced to roll on the one or two pieces of armor we need.  Likewise, people that are newer or don't have the time to attend each event are being punished if a merit system in instituted.  I have no doubt a system can be established that makes each party happy. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#FFFF00>- </font><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bsaryrnguildallianceboard>saryrnguildallianceboard</a><font color=#FFFF00> - </font><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fsaryrnguildallianceboardfrm1>General Discussion</a> <font color=#FFFF00> - </font><br><br><table border=0 align=center><tr><td align=center><a href="http://www.qksrv.net/click-553273-1925262" target="_blank" >
